1+Tr(C)x+\det(C)x^2=\det(I+xC)
A=(I+Cx)B(I+C^tx)=B+BC^tx+CBx+CBC^tx^2=B+(CB+BC^T)x+CBC^Tx^2
\det(A)=\det(B)\det(I+Cx)\det((I+Cx)^T)=\det B(\det(I+Cx))^2=\det B(1+Tr(C) x+\det(C)x^2)
